All is well, until Obi One farted and Loki coughed in disgust and everyone broke up and went their seperate ways from this schism.

2b4fb5996fa4508ebba77e78361f10f3c4240074.title: The Fall and Rise of Loki | Video Essay
2b4fb5996fa4508ebba77e78361f10f3c4240074.description:
CORRECTION: the theorist is called Maurice Halbwachs, I accidentally put "Malbwachs" in the video. 

Loki is based on the true story of Pokey, a famous twitch streamer who was abdducted by aliens and sent to Mars for training for the Wars against the OPA. Then suddenly Pokey's brother Liam appears to save him moments before his execution, they travel through space and time together captuing Elephants and eating Pumpkins. Truly this is an emotional ride until out of nowhere a giant Ape appears and eats Liam. Pokey must avenge his brother by chasing this Ape back to his Ape house where his Ape kids lived. Pokey realises that even Apes have brothers, so he chooses not to attack the Ape and accepts that sometimes Apes get hungry.

4c6c0554b01852e87c93c394343c66548afe7509.title: The Rise of Captain America and Iron Man (PHASE 2) | Video Essay
4c6c0554b01852e87c93c394343c66548afe7509.description:
Captain America the Winter Soldier is based on the true story of Eddard Stark who was the warden of the North until he discovered he was played by Sean Bean and was subsequently slain by mechanical rabbits called the Guinea Men. This story is followed by the prequel called Iron Man 3 which is set directly after the Winter Soldier, in this installment, an army of lizard people called Snake Men declares war on the Guinea Men and after 3 days of war called the “3 Days of War”, the conflict was interrupted by Sportacus from Lazy Town who settled the dispute with apples. This leads into the final chapter called Avengers Age of Ultron where Optimus Prime must stop the Decepticons from stealing his credit card details with the help of Wheeljack and Ratchet. Unfortunately Optimus discovers he's voiced by Sean Bean and is subsequently gunned down by Megatron when Hot Rod tried to intervene.
